duties_responsibilities.duty: Serve as a single entry or 'easy access' point to help members and providers navigate through managed care.
Apply knowledge of applicable regulations, identify resources, and eliminate barriers for members and providers.
Provide care management interventions and seamless support across transitions of care.
Conduct face-to-face visits with members in their home and intermittent meetings onsite.

education_certification.credential: Associate's degree in a health care related field (BSN preferred)
